item.title: 【Requests】[REQ VID] - Winx Club Nickelodeon Dub Season 3, 4, and Specials (Prime Video RIP)
item.description:
Hello, I'm looking for someone to rip the Nickelodeon dub of Winx Club from Prime Video, specifically Seasons 3, 4, and the TV Specials. The iTunes Versions have been mostly taken down (the specials remain), but it remains up on Prime Video for purchase. I am not sure how long it will be up for since Rainbow has purchased Viacom's share in them back.
